(30, 'SUNGBOON EDITOR Deep Collagen Serum | 5% Volufiline + 58% Low Molecular Collagen + 2% Niacinamide | Hydrating & Smoothing Face Serum | Korean Skincare, 1.01 fl oz | Gifts for Women', 'sungboon-editor-deep-collagen-serum-5-volufiline-58-low-molecular-collagen-2-niacinamide-hydrating-smoothing-face-serum-korean-skincare-101-fl-oz-gifts-for-women', 'SUNGBOON EDITOR', 'Beauty & Personal Care', 'Amazon USA', 4086.00, 3720.00, 1, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/D1gDLu3VHkc0u2i3QFVYBLg48XRXxgnRlOMqy3p1.png', '<h2><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>[Lightweight Collagen Care] By utilizing ultra-low molecular weight French collagen of less than 300 daltons, this serum absorbs smoothly and feels lightweight on the skin, unlike regular collagen. It helps support a comfortable, hydrated feel and supports skin elasticity.</li><li>[NIACINAMIDE-ENRICHED FORMULA] Infused with niacinamide to help balance skin texture and tone, while providing hydration for a radiant glow.</li><li>[Plump-looking Care] Formulated with Volufiline to help support skin elasticity care and create a firm-looking, plump-looking appearance while smoothing the appearance of fine lines.</li><li>[SAFE FOR SENSITIVE SKIN] Offers deep hydration while remaining gentle for sensitive and dry skin, providing conditioning care without irritation.</li><li>[THE PERFECT SKINCARE GIFT] Ideal for dry, sensitive, or dull or tired-looking skin, this beautifully packaged Korean skincare essential makes a thoughtful gift for anyone who loves glowing skin.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'SUNGBOON EDITOR Deep Collagen Serum | 5% Volufiline + 58% Low Molecular Collagen + 2% Niacinamide | Hydrating & Smoothing Face Serum | Korean Skincare, 1.01 fl oz | Gifts for Women', 'SUNGBOON EDITOR Deep Collagen Serum | 5% Volufiline + 58% Low Molecular Collagen + 2% Niacinamide | Hydrating & Smoothing Face Serum | Korean Skincare, 1.01 fl oz | Gifts for Women | Amazon USA', 'Shop SUNGBOON EDITOR Deep Collagen Serum | 5% Volufiline + 58% Low Molecular Collagen + 2% Niacinamide | Hydrating & Smoothing Face Serum | Korean Skincare, 1.01 fl oz | Gifts for Women. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-11 16:52:50', '2026-04-11 16:53:10'),
(31, 'Micro Ingredients Vitamin D3 50,000 IU + K2 MK-7 200 mcg, 240 Softgels | Virgin Coconut Oil | 2-in-1 Support | Easy to Swallow, Non-GMO', 'micro-ingredients-vitamin-d3-50000-iu-k2-mk-7-200-mcg-240-softgels-virgin-coconut-oil-2-in-1-support-easy-to-swallow-non-gmo', 'Micro Ingredients', 'Medicine and Supplements', NULL, 7200.00, 6199.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/ubclCfeYZBz7XeWoU4kbGUgiWfzduQLDrLBDjRZG.png', '<h2><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>Micro Ingredients offers max strength 2 in 1 vitamin D3 + K2 coconut oil softgels. An efficiently absorbed formula that contains D3 as cholecalciferol and K2 in its top grade menaquinone (MK7) form. Only requires one softgel per week.</li><li>Enjoy a family size of 240 easy-to-consume mini coconut oil infused softgels. A potent once per week complex that can be shared with multiple family members. 50,000 iu Vitamin D3 and 200 mcg vitamin K2 per dose.</li><li>Vitamin D3 + K2 are essential micronutrients for adults that work together to support proper calcium absorption to our bones and teeth, while also promoting joint health, immune defense, and heart function.</li><li>Fat soluble vitamins like D and K are absorbed more completely when a fat source is present. The addition of the healthy MCT coconut oil offers the perfect fat for maximum nutrient bioavailability.</li><li>Premium non-GMO vitamin D3 + K2 supplements. Made without soy, dairy, gluten, preservatives, and flavors. Ingredients must pass our 3rd party lab tests to ensure a product that is safe, pure, and potent.</li><li>With 240 softgels per bag, this value pack is designed to support wellness for the whole family.</li><li>Expiration date is printed on the back of the product package.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Micro Ingredients Vitamin D3 50,000 IU + K2 MK-7 200 mcg, 240 Softgels | Virgin Coconut Oil | 2-in-1 Support | Easy to Swallow, Non-GMO', 'Micro Ingredients Vitamin D3 50,000 IU + K2 MK-7 200 mcg, 240 Softgels | Virgin Coconut Oil | 2-in-1 Support | Easy to Swallow, Non-GMO', 'Shop Micro Ingredients Vitamin D3 50,000 IU + K2 MK-7 200 mcg, 240 Softgels | Virgin Coconut Oil | 2-in-1 Support | Easy to Swallow, Non-GMO. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-11 16:55:31', '2026-04-28 13:03:32'),
(32, 'Crazyquick Padel Shoes', 'crazyquick-padel-shoes', 'Crazyquick', 'Shoes', 'Adidas', 19163.98, 13764.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/IrCjSYGXEXFTcWI4Vay8628ibaSRRmkebq5ztW9R.png', '<h2><strong>adidas Crazyquick Padel Shoes (Key Highlights)</strong></h2><ul><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ultra-Lightweight:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> adidas\' lightest padel shoe, built for maximum speed and agility.</span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Lightstrike Cushioning:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Low-profile midsole for high energy return and quick responsiveness.</span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Superior Stability:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Features a </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Slingframe</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> construction to support the foot during fast lateral pivots.</span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Durable Outsole:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Adiwear</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> rubber provides excellent grip on padel courts and prevents early wear.</span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Breathable Upper:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Mesh material keeps your feet cool during intense matches.</span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Reinforced Toe:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Adituff</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> technology protects the front area from dragging and scuffing.</span></li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Crazyquick Padel Shoes', 'Crazyquick Padel Shoes | Adidas', 'Shop Crazyquick Padel Shoes. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 17:39:28', '2026-04-1