(33, 'Qunol Magnesium Capsules 420mg, High Absorption Magnesium Supplement, Extra Strength, Bone and Muscle Health Supplement, 120 Count', 'qunol-magnesium-glycinate-complex-gentle-on-stomach-250mg-one-pill-dose-superior-absorption-magnesium-nerve-bone-and-muscle-health-supplement-60-count-pack-of-1', 'Qunol Magnesium', 'Medicine and Supplements', 'Amazon USA', 3241.00, 2499.00, 10, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/LQN9hJoeKnuhZdvrGIUMxsaUCz42bPocbNYlgNrP.png', '<h2 style=\"font-family: Cinzel, Bangla342, serif;\"><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>MAGNESIUM GLYCINATE COMPLEX - Qunol Ultra Magnesium combines magnesium glycinate and magnesium glycerophosphate, two forms of high-absorption magnesium</li><li>GENTLE ON THE STOMACH - Other brands use magnesium oxide in order to increase the potency, however, Qunol Ultra Magnesium only uses high-absorption forms of magnesium that don\'t cause stomach distress</li><li>ONE PILL DOSE - By combining two forms of high absorption magnesium, Qunol Ultra Magnesium is able to provide 250mg of elemental magnesium in a single pill. Many other brands require up to 4 pills per serving</li><li>NERVE, BONE and MUSCLE HEALTH - Magnesium is involved in muscle contractions, nerve impulses, energy metabolism, and protein formation</li><li>CLEAN INGREDIENTS - Gluten Free, Vegan, Non-GMO and No Artificial Dyes in order to meet your dietary needs</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Qunol Magnesium Capsules 420mg, High Absorption Magnesium Supplement, Extra Strength, Bone and Muscle Health Supplement, 120 Count', 'Qunol Magnesium Capsules 420mg, High Absorption Magnesium Supplement, Extra Strength, Bone and Muscle Health Supplement, 120 Count | Amazon USA', 'Shop Qunol Magnesium Glycinate Complex, Gentle on Stomach, 250mg One Pill Dose, Superior-Absorption Magnesium, Nerve, Bone and Muscle Health Supplement, 60 Count (Pack of 1). High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 17:44:19', '2026-04-14 14:21:11'),
