ilajit supplement is presented in its pure, minimally processed form, free from heavy metals, fillers, additives, and suitable for vegans. Using the included copper spoon, simply scoop a pea-sized amount and stir it into water or milk until fully dissolved, making it a hassle-free addition to your daily routine. Use it daily for 2-3 months for better results</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Better Alt Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin Pack of 1 High Potency Gold Grade 75 Servings for Energy Boost & Immune Support, 85+ Trace Minerals, 75%+ Fulvic Acid, with Lab Test Report,400 mg', 'Better Alt Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin Pack of 1 High Potency Gold Grade 75 Servings for Energy Boost & Immune Support, 85+ Trace Minerals, 75%+ Fulvic Acid, with Lab Test Report,400 mg | Amazon USA', 'Shop Better Alt Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin Pack of 1 High Potency Gold Grade 75 Servings for Energy Boost & Immune Support, 85+ Trace Minerals, 75%+ Fulvic Acid, with Lab Test Report,400 mg. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 17:49:55', '2026-04-12 17:51:04'),
