ic Naturals Ultimate Omega, Lemon Flavor - 90 Soft Gels - 1280 mg Omega-3 - High-Potency Omega-3 Fish Oil Supplement with EPA & DHA - Promotes Brain & Heart Health - Non-GMO - 45 Servings. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 17:53:09', '2026-04-12 17:53:33');
