(36, 'Lansinoh Lanolin Nipple Cream Safe for Breastfeeding Baby, 100% Natural Nipple Butter, Breastfeeding Essentials for Postpartum Moms, 1.41 Ounces', 'lansinoh-lanolin-nipple-cream-safe-for-breastfeeding-baby-100-natural-nipple-butter-breastfeeding-essentials-for-postpartum-moms-141-ounces', 'Lansinoh Lanolin', 'Beauty & Personal Care', 'Amazon USA', 2149.00, 1866.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/qGhWOgWLGr3kUz1bwin3ndYoHH8GndmeDPVKf017.png', '<h2><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>100% NATURAL AND SAFE FOR BABY– No need to remove lansinoh nipple cream before breastfeeding. Made with a single natural ingredient, and never any petroleum, parabens, fragrance, or taste</li><li>SOOTHES SORE NIPPLES (AND MORE!) – Rich, spreadable Lanolin Nipple Cream provides soothing protection for your sore, delicate skin. Also use as a lip balm, or to soften cuticles and dry heels.</li><li>DERMATOLOGICALLY TESTED – Comfort you can trust. Dermatologically tested, doctor recommended, and safe for sensitive skin</li><li>ULTRA-PURE AND HYPOALLERGENIC – Created by nature, made better through science. Our unique purification process ensures you get only pure, hypoallergenic nipple balm with no additives or preservatives</li><li>ETHICALLY SOURCED – Comfort for your nipples and your conscience. Our lanolin is ethically sourced, never tested on animals, and certified climate neutral. We’re doing our part for mothers everywhere – including mother earth</li><li>MOM APPROVED - For over 40 years moms have been using Lansinoh lanolin. Approved by many nursing moms, our lanolin nipple balm is one of Lansinoh\'s top baby registry items</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Lansinoh Lanolin Nipple Cream Safe for Breastfeeding Baby, 100% Natural Nipple Butter, Breastfeeding Essentials for Postpartum Moms, 1.41 Ounces', 'Lansinoh Lanolin Nipple Cream Safe for Breastfeeding Baby, 100% Natural Nipple Butter, Breastfeeding Essentials for Postpartum Moms, 1.41 Ounces | Amazon USA', 'Shop Lansinoh Lanolin Nipple Cream Safe for Breastfeeding Baby, 100% Natural Nipple Butter, Breastfeeding Essentials for Postpartum Moms, 1.41 Ounces. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 17:56:07', '2026-04-12 17:56:39'),
(37, 'Amazon Kindle Paperwhite 16GB (newest model) – 20% faster, with new 7\" glare-free display and weeks of battery life – Black', 'amazon-kindle-paperwhite-16gb-newest-model-20-faster-with-new-7-glare-free-display-and-weeks-of-battery-life-black', 'Amazon Kindle', 'Gadget & Gear', 'Amazon USA', 28684.98, 25620.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/NJHPLuz1DxcSOap04JDhCAElXCvjwnwcNSwRL5Yy.png', '<ul><li>Our fastest Kindle Paperwhite ever – The next-generation 7“ Paperwhite display has a higher contrast ratio and 25% faster page turns.</li><li>Ready for travel – The ultra-thin design has a larger glare-free screen so pages stay sharp no matter where you are.</li><li>Escape into your books – Your Kindle doesn’t have social media, notifications, or other distracting apps.</li><li>Battery life for your longest novel – A single charge via USB-C lasts up to 12 weeks.</li><li>Read in any light – Adjust the display from white to amber to read in bright sunlight or in the dark.</li><li>Waterproof and worry-free – Take your stories by the pool, in the bath, or anywhere in between.</li><li>Massive selection – Instantly access over 15 million titles in the Kindle Store worldwide, and add a Kindle Unlimited subscription for all-you-can read access to a catalog including best sellers.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Amazon Kindle Paperwhite 16GB (newest model) – 20% faster, with new 7\" glare-free display and weeks of battery life – Black', 'Amazon Kindle Paperwhite 16GB (newest model) – 20% faster, with new 7\" glare-free display and weeks of battery life – Black | Amazon USA', 'Shop Amazon Kindle Paperwhite 16GB (newest model) – 20% faster, with new 7\" glare-free display and weeks of battery life – Black. High quality product with great features.', '2026-04-12 18:01:01', '2026-04-12 18:01:41'),
(38, 'Micro Ingredients Pure Magnesium Complex, 300 Capsules | Triple Magnesium Glycinate, Malate, Taurate with Vitamin C | 100% Chelated | Supports Muscles, Nerves, & Energy | Only Active Ingredients', 'micro-ingredients-pure-magnesium-complex-300-capsules-triple-magnesium-glycinate-malate-taurate-with-vitamin-c-100-chelated-supports-muscles-nerves-energy-only-active-ingredients', 'Micro_Ingredients', 'Health Care', 'Amazon USA', 4260.00, 3494.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/mrVKVeAe9zK87CAUKJ7AQJn3X9eJtfhztGmmixoo.png', '<h2><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>Micro Ingredients offers a pure 4-in-1 Triple Magnesium Complex combined with vitamin C for enhanced antioxidant support. A capsuled formula that features raw, active ingredients with no fillers.</li><li>Each bottle contains 300 capsules, delivering an extra strength 400mg dose of pure magnesium glycinate, malate, taurate, and vitamin C. Every 3-capsule serving provides a 100-day supply.</li><li>Magnesium, known as the “master mineral,” is an essential trace mineral that plays a crucial role in hundreds of cellular functions. Including support for muscle, energy, immune, and heart health.</li><li>Enjoy only active ingredients that use high bioavailable chelated minerals and easily absorbed fat-soluble vitamins.</li><li>Premium non-GMO magnesium supplements. Made without fillers, soy, dairy, gluten, fish, shellfish, peanuts, and tree nuts. Ingredients must pass our 3rd party lab tests to ensure a product that is safe, pure, and potent.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'Micro Ingredients Pure Magnesium Complex, 300 Capsules | Triple Magnesium Glycinate, Malate, Taurate with Vitamin C | 100% Chelated | Supports Muscles, Nerves, & Energy | Only Active Ingredients', 'Micro Ingredients Pure Magnesium Complex, 300 Capsules | Triple Magnesium Glycinate, Malate, Taurate with Vitamin C | 100% Chelated | Supports Muscles, Nerves, & Energy | Only Active Ingredients | Amazon USA', 'Shop Micro Ingre