features.', '2026-04-18 16:29:21', '2026-04-27 23:13:51'),
(66, 'One A Day Multivitamin for Women- Daily Vitamins for Woman with Biotin, Calcium, Folic Acid, Iron & Zinc, Complete Women’s Vitamins, 200 Ct (Packaging May Vary)', 'one-a-day-multivitamin-for-women-daily-vitamins-for-woman-with-biotin-calcium-folic-acid-iron-zinc-complete-womens-vitamins-200-ct-packaging-may-vary', 'One A Day Multivitamin', 'Health Care', 'Amazon USA', 3387.00, 2887.00, 20, 0.00, 0, 1, 'published', NULL, 'products/images/hmJmJhuK0BsoIXtcetsjFqFPRPo4OkAnkiS1vEJr.png', '<h2><strong>About this item</strong></h2><ul><li>Nutritional support for women: One A Day womens multivitamin is specially formulated with key nutrients to support 6 key vital functions:* physical energy(1), heart health (2), immune health, bone health, skin health, and healthy muscle function</li><li>Rich in 17 nutrients: Women daily multivitamin formulated with key nutrients including Iron, Vitamins A, C &amp; E, all 8 B Vitamins, and more, for nutritional support</li><li>Women’s vitamins designed by experts: Over 80 years of expertise designing science backed formulas​​. Decades of expertise with quality nutrients that women can count on</li><li>Free of what you don’t want: Our women’s multivitamin is free of 9 major US food allergens: no egg allergen, no dairy (milk) allergen, no soy allergen, no fish and no crustacean shellfish allergens, no peanut and no tree nut allergens, no sesame allergen, no soy allergen</li><li>How to take: Adults: take one tablet daily, with food. A convenient, women multivitamin to provide nutritional support for your health*</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'One A Day Multivitamin for Women- Daily Vitamins for Woman with Biotin, Calcium, Folic Acid, Iron & Zinc, Complete Women’s Vitamins, 200 Ct (Packaging May Vary)', 'One A Day Multivitamin for Women- Daily Vitamins for Woman with Biotin, Calcium, Folic Acid, Iron & Zinc, Complete Women’s Vitamins, 200 Ct (Packaging May Vary) | Amazon USA', 'Shop One A Day Multivitamin for Women- Daily Vitamins for Woman wit